Description: 
        gherkindb
        --------
        
        gherkindb is lightweight, fast, and simple database based on pickledb
        
        ```````````````
        
        ::
        
        import gherkindb
        
        db = gherkindb.load('test1.db', True)
        
        db.set('key', 'value')
        
        # Outputs: value
        print(db.get('key'))
        
        # Added serialization functionality
        def my_func():
            print("Much better!")
        
        db.sset('func', my_func)
        
        # Outputs: Much better!
        db.sget('func')()
        
        # Also :
        
        # Outputs: Much better!
        reborn = db.sget('func')
        
        reborn()
        
        
        And Easy to Install
        ```````````````````
        
        ::
        
            $ pip3 install gherkindb
        
        
        
